5. Risk Score System
5.1 Risk Score Formula (Two Step)
The Two Step formula accounts for the dual-phase structure by averaging the targets:

riskScore = ((target1 + target2) / 200) * (split / 100)
           / ((dailyLoss / 100) * (maxLoss / 100))

// Loss type multipliers (same as One Step):
if (dailyLossType === 'eod')      riskScore *= 0.85
if (maxLossType === 'eod')        riskScore *= 0.85
if (dailyLossType === 'intraday') riskScore *= 1.10
if (maxLossType === 'intraday')   riskScore *= 1.10

NOTE: The simulator formula does not include minDays in the denominator. Only target, split, dailyLoss, maxLoss with loss type multipliers.
5.2 Risk Score Thresholds & Actions
Score Range	Risk Level	Protection	Actions
< 0.5	Critical	Maximum	Enhanced monitoring, daily limits -20%, manual review
0.5 - 0.8	High	Maximum	Aggressive config warning, extra monitoring
0.8 - 1.5	Medium	High	Standard operations
> 1.5	Low	Moderate	Fast payouts, scaling +2x bonus
6. Trading Rules & Freedoms
6.1 Maximum Freedoms
The Two Step Challenge offers the most permissive trading environment:

Feature	Status	Conditions
News Trading	ALLOWED	5-minute buffer if daily loss > 5% AND config is flagged as risky
Weekend Holding	ALLOWED	No restrictions (unlike One Step which requires min days >= 5)
EA / Bots	ALLOWED	All types including semi-HFT; only pure latency-arb blocked
Copy Trading	ALLOWED	No verification required (unlike One Step)
All Instruments	ALLOWED	Forex, indices, commodities, crypto, metals
Hedging	ALLOWED	Both intra-account and cross-account hedging permitted
6.2 Consistency Rule
Applied identically to each phase independently. No single trading day's profit can exceed X% of that phase's total profit.
Range: 10% - 50% (default: 30%). Weekly payout caps at 30%.
6.3 Minimum Performance Thresholds
Metric	Min Required	Applied Per
Sharpe Ratio	0.5	Each phase independently
Win Rate	30%	Each phase independently
Total Trades	4 x Phase Min Days	Each phase independently
7. Payout & Scaling System
7.1 Payout Parameters
Parameter	Two Step Value	vs One Step
Minimum Profit for Payout	1% of account balance	More accessible (vs 2%)
Payout Frequencies	Monthly ($0) / Bi-Weekly (+$29) / Weekly (+$59)	Same pricing
Maximum Scaling	10x after validation	2x higher (vs 5x)
7.2 Payout Velocity Control
maxMonthlyPayout = accountSize * (1 / riskScore) * 0.2

// With 10x scaling, the effective max is much higher:
// $100K account scaled to $1M, Risk Score 1.2:
// Max = $1,000,000 * (1/1.2) * 0.2 = $166,667/month
7.3 Scaling Milestones
Milestone	Scale Factor	Account Size ($100K base)	Requirements
Initial Funded	1x	$100,000	Pass Phase 1 + Phase 2
After 1st month	1.5x	$150,000	Positive P&L, no breaches
After 3 months	2.5x	$250,000	Consistent profitability
After 6 months	5x	$500,000	Risk score > 1.0, low drawdown
After 12 months	10x	$1,000,000	Elite trader status
7.4 Progressive Configuration Lock
Milestone	Customizable Options	Locked Parameters
Pre-Payout	100%	None
After 1st Payout	75%	Max daily loss reduced by 1%
After 3rd Payout	50%	Both profit targets + consistency locked
 
8. Database Schema
8.1 Evaluations Table (Two Step Extension)
CREATE TABLE evaluations_two_step (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users(id),
  type ENUM('two_step') NOT NULL,
  account_size DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('phase1','phase2','passed','failed','funded'),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),

  -- Dual-Phase Targets
  profit_target_1 DECIMAL NOT NULL,       -- Phase 1: 5-12%
  profit_target_2 DECIMAL NOT NULL,       -- Phase 2: 3-8%
  combined_target DECIMAL GENERATED ALWAYS AS
    (profit_target_1 + profit_target_2) STORED,

  -- Shared Risk Parameters
  daily_loss DECIMAL NOT NULL,            -- 3-8%
  max_loss DECIMAL NOT NULL,              -- 6-15%
  profit_split DECIMAL NOT NULL,          -- 70-90%
  min_days_total INTEGER NOT NULL,        -- 5-20
  min_days_phase1 INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS
    (CEIL(min_days_total * 0.6)) STORED,
  min_days_phase2 INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS
    (min_days_total - CEIL(min_days_total * 0.6)) STORED,
  consistency_rule DECIMAL NOT NULL,      -- 10-50%
  daily_loss_type ENUM('intraday','eod','static'),
  max_loss_type ENUM('intraday','eod','static'),
  payout_frequency ENUM('monthly','biweekly','weekly'),
  overnight_holding BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  overweek_holding BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,

  -- Phase Tracking
  current_phase INTEGER DEFAULT 1,
  phase1_start_date TIMESTAMP,
  phase1_end_date TIMESTAMP,
  phase2_start_date TIMESTAMP,
  phase2_end_date TIMESTAMP,
  funded_date TIMESTAMP,

  -- Pricing
  base_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  difficulty_adj DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  split_adj DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  options_adj DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  loss_type_adj DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  equal_loss_surcharge DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  payout_freq_adj DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  promo_code VARCHAR(20),
  promo_discount DECIMAL DEFAULT 0,
  final_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,

  -- Real-time Metrics (per current phase)
  risk_score DECIMAL,
  current_balance DECIMAL,
  peak_balance DECIMAL,
  total_trades INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  profitable_days INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  scale_factor DECIMAL DEFAULT 1.0
);
8.2 Phase History Table
CREATE TABLE phase_history (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  evaluation_id UUID REFERENCES evaluations_two_step(id),
  phase_number INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 1 or 2
  start_date TIMESTAMP,
  end_date TIMESTAMP,
  result ENUM('passed','failed'),
  final_balance DECIMAL,
  total_trades INTEGER,
  profitable_days INTEGER,
  best_day_pct DECIMAL,
  sharpe_ratio DECIMAL,
  win_rate DECIMAL
);
8.3 Promo Codes Table
CREATE TABLE promo_codes (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  code VARCHAR(20) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  discount_type ENUM('percent','fixed') NOT NULL,
  discount_value DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  label VARCHAR(100),
  is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
  max_uses INTEGER,
  current_uses INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  valid_from TIMESTAMP,
  valid_until TIMESTAMP,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
9. API Endpoints
All One Step endpoints apply, plus the following Two Step-specific endpoints:

Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/evaluations/configure	Validate config with dual targets, return price
POST	/api/evaluations/purchase	Create two-step evaluation account
GET	/api/evaluations/{id}/phase-status	Get current phase, progress, and requirements
POST	/api/evaluations/{id}/advance-phase	Trigger Phase 1 -> Phase 2 transition
GET	/api/evaluations/{id}/phase-history	Retrieve completed phase results
GET	/api/evaluations/{id}/risk-score	Current risk score
GET	/api/evaluations/{id}/scaling	Current scale factor and next milestone
POST	/api/payouts/request	Submit payout (min 1% profit)
GET	/api/payouts/eligibility	Check payout eligibility with velocity limits
POST	/api/promo/validate	Validate a promo code and return discount details
GET	/api/promo/{code}/check	Check if a promo code is valid and active
10. Kill Switches & Firm Protection
Trigger	Threshold	Action
Daily Firm Loss	2% of total firm capital	HALT_ALL_TRADING
Account Correlation	20+ correlated accounts	SUSPEND_ACCOUNTS
Drawdown Cascade	30% simultaneous drawdown	REVIEW_MODE
Phase Skip Attempt	Any attempt to bypass Phase 1	IMMEDIATE_BAN
Scale Abuse	Rapid scaling with minimal activity	FREEZE_SCALING + review
10.1 Configuration Cooldown
7-day cooldown: Same parameter combo blocked for 7 days after failure.
Monthly limit: Maximum 3 configurations per calendar month.
Post-funded change: Configuration change after funded status triggers full reset (both phases).
11. Gamification & Trader Levels
Same level system as One Step. Two Step-specific achievements:

Achievement	Trigger	Reward
First Payout	Complete first payout	+5% bonus on next challenge
Consistent Trader	3 consecutive profitable months	Split +5%
Risk Master	Risk score > 1.5 for 30 days	Fees -10%
Diamond Hands	Never enter drawdown	Scaling bonus
Phase Speedster	Pass both phases in < 50% of allowed time	Express badge + priority support
10x Legend	Reach maximum 10x scaling	Lifetime VIP status
12. One Step vs Two Step - Quick Comparison
Feature	One Step	Two Step
Evaluation Phases	1	2 (sequential)
Base Price ($100K)	$499	$399
Profit Target	5-15% single	P1: 5-12% + P2: 3-8%
Daily Loss Range	2-8%	3-8%
Max Loss Range	4-12%	6-15%
Split Range	50-90%	70-90%
Split Baseline	70%	80%
Split Rate	$4 per %	$6 per %
Min Days	3-10	5-20 (60/40 split)
Max Scaling	5x	10x
Min Payout	2% profit	1% profit
Payout Freq Pricing	Monthly $0 / Bi-Weekly +$29 / Weekly +$59	Same
News Trading	Conditional	Allowed (with buffer)
Copy Trading	With verification	Unrestricted
Intraday Loss Adj	-$15 each	-$19 each
Static Loss Adj	+$25 each (premium)	+$29 each (premium)
EOD Loss Adj	$0 each (baseline)	$0 each (baseline)
Overnight Add-On	+$19	+$25
Overweek Add-On	+$29	+$39
Equal Loss Surcharge	+$100	+$100
Promo Code Floor	Base * 0.3	Base * 0.3

